WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.700 --> 00:00:10.012
Our mission is to transform ordinary homes into wellness homes. Spaces that keep you, your family, and the planet safe.

2
00:00:11.812 --> 00:00:21.604
Magppie is not a kitchen company. It is a wellness movement. We sell health, safety, and twenty-five years of peace of mind.

3
00:00:23.404 --> 00:00:32.668
Magppie Group has been in business for over fifty years. For more than twenty of those, we have been creating kitchens and wardrobes.

4
00:00:34.468 --> 00:00:43.180
Our first SilverStone kitchen was installed in late twenty sixteen, giving us more than nine years of real-world performance validation.

5
00:00:44.980 --> 00:00:52.804
Today, Magppie is expanding globally, with a new store recently opened in Florida, in the United States.

6
00:00:54.604 --> 00:01:03.772
At KBIS twenty twenty-six in Orlando, the world's largest kitchen show, Magppie won the Most Unexpected Innovation award.

7
00:01:05.572 --> 00:01:14.860
Magppie wellness kitchens are made entirely from our patented sanitised stone. Zero percent wood, so no trees are cut.

8
00:01:16.660 --> 00:01:25.948
And no harmful toxins like formaldehyde are released into your home. The stone contains real silver and copper nano-particles.

9
00:01:27.748 --> 00:01:36.724
That makes your kitchen naturally anti-bacterial and anti-fungal. It is termite-proof, waterproof, and fire-safe.

10
00:01:38.524 --> 00:01:46.660
Every kitchen comes with a twenty-five year unconditional guarantee, plus twenty-five complimentary annual services.

11
00:01:48.460 --> 00:01:59.836
SilverStone is our patented wellness stone. We take porcelain clay, heat it to thirteen hundred degrees, and infuse it with silver and copper nano-particles.

12
00:02:01.636 --> 00:02:15.580
This makes it anti-bacterial, anti-fungal, non-porous, stain-proof, scratch-resistant, and impact-resistant. It is one hundred percent food-grade. You can eat directly off it.

13
00:02:17.380 --> 00:02:26.404
It is stronger than granite and more elegant than marble. And because it is engineered, not mined, it does not harm the environment.

14
00:02:28.204 --> 00:02:34.996
Remember the key phrase. It looks like a stone, but it does not behave like a regular stone.

15
00:02:36.796 --> 00:02:48.676
Seven safety pillars, always in order. Stain safe, coffee, haldi and oil wipe off easily. Scratch safe, daily chopping leaves no marks.

16
00:02:50.476 --> 00:02:59.908
High load bearing, drawers support up to sixty kilograms each. Fire safe, the stone does not catch fire or spread flames.

17
00:03:01.708 --> 00:03:09.124
Water safe. In a thirty-day water test, wood swelled and weakened while the stone stayed unchanged.

18
00:03:10.924 --> 00:03:20.164
Impact safe, a heavy ceramic jar drop leaves it intact. And up to sixty-two percent more storage than standard kitchens.

19
00:03:21.964 --> 00:03:30.820
The award was presented by our director of U S operations, Kishor Rico, on February seventeenth, twenty twenty-six.

20
00:03:32.620 --> 00:03:45.340
Magppie kitchens are trusted by some of India's most respected families. Mukesh Ambani and Anant Ambani of Reliance. Cricketers M S Dhoni and Harbhajan Singh.

21
00:03:47.140 --> 00:03:59.548
Actors Ranbir Kapoor, Shilpa Shetty, Chiranjeevi, and Akhil Akkineni. And business leaders like Peyush Bansal of Lenskart, and Rizwan Sajan of the Danube group.

22
00:04:01.348 --> 00:04:07.684
Magppie. A wellness movement, fifty years in the making. Welcome home.

